hashtag.indices

hashtag.indices: [number]

Implementation of HashtagInterface.hashtag.indices

  • Defined in models/Hashtag.ts:22

An array of integers indicating the offsets within the Tweet text where the hashtag begins and ends. The first integer represents the location of the # character in the Tweet text string. The second integer represents the location of the first character after the hashtag.

type

{[number]}
